            <p>Many customers report feeling 25 years younger after taking Karen Phytoplankton. Benefits include increased energy, better sleep, improved digestion, and overall wellness. The supplement provides pure source nutrition directly to your cells, which can help address foundational nutritional deficiencies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-amber-100 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-800 shadow-md">
          <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800">Is there a guarantee?</h3>
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-800 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
